"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-02-18-French-Riviera-s-Menton-celebrates-Olympic-year-with-Lemon-Festival-1ri62RkMixq-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copied  Menton marked the Olympic year by showcasing lush citrus during a two-week carnival-style festival with giant floats and sculptures of swimmers, tennis, rugby and badminton players, all assembled from lemons and oranges.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8206337602459936e-15, \"text\": \"Menton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year's edition of the annual Lemon Festival, the 90th, celebrates the Paris Olympic Games and was called \\\"Olympia a Menton.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dAbout 140 tonnes of citrus fruits and nearly 500,000 citruses were used to build and maintain the floats and historical scenes that line the central Bioves Park.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers expect up to 200,000 visitors this year.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 1